25|$|Headlight {{flashing}} in India {{is often used}} as a signal that the driver flashing you is offering {{to let you go}} first. Such use is however strongly discouraged because it can lead to accidents where the driver flashing has not seen the approach of another <b>road</b> <b>user.</b> It is also used to indicate to an oncoming vehicle to either stop or give way in narrow lanes.|$|E
